    - target: {fileID: 3177037010239792799, guid: 80e520690f98a45cd96165b79d262b34, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'The game allows you to determine the outcome of the story by the sum
        of choices you''re making. The way you react or respond to situations can
        influence your opinions of other people and their opinions of you, reveal
        clues and unveil different scenarios.


        There are no clear indications
        of right and wrong, but you can refer to your findings and the people you
        meet through your inventory and your profile list, respectively.


        Controls:


        ''M''
        : The game menu.


        ''I'': See your inventory and click on the items
        for information.


        ''A'': Check your attributes and XP points. You
        can use XP to upgrade skills displayed on the right skillbar.


        ''P'': 
        A synopsis of the characters you''ve met so far.


        ''S'': Your collection
        of statements and evidence. The more the story progresses, the more you will
        need to refer to them, in order to keep track and make the "right" decisions.


        Remember,
        you have a mystery to solve, but it''s up to you whether you''ll succeed
        or not. In any case, you better watch your back...'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
